<i>adjective</i>: 번화하다 [번화하다], 번성하다 [번성하다], 강성하다 [강성하다] <i>noun</i>: 흥성 [흥성], 번성 [번성] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번화하다 [번화하다]</dt><br>
<dd>bustling; thriving</dd><br>
<dd>상업 활동이 활발하고 화려하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Splendid and active in commercial activities.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번성하다 [번성하다]</dt><br>
<dd>thriving</dd><br>
<dd>나무나 풀이 자라서 우거져 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Trees or grass having grown thick.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>강성하다 [강성하다]</dt><br>
<dd>powerful; mighty; thriving</dd><br>
<dd>세력이 강하고 한창 활발하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being strong, influential, active, and thriving.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흥성 [흥성]</dt><br>
<dd>prosperity; thriving</dd><br>
<dd>기운 차게 일어나거나 세력이 대단히 커져서 널리 퍼짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a group, country, etc., rising strongly or becoming powerful, with widening influence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번성 [번성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. prosperity; thriving</dd><br>
<dd>세력이 커져서 널리 퍼짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's force grows and prevails.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flourishing; luxuriance</dd><br>
<dd>나무나 풀이 자라서 우거져 있음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which trees and plants grow profusely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>